channel.title: Request a PHP script
channel.description:
Hey, ive made a sight basically to help me develop my PHP skills a little. It expanded a bit since the original thought, as theres a few [url=http://www.fanabu.com/articles.php]articles[/url] there now too.
Anyway feel free to [url=http://fanabu.com/request.php]request a PHP script[/url]. Make sure to browse the [url=http://www.fanabu.com/resources.php]resources section[/url] first to make sure the script hasnt already been produced
